---
title: Spicy Coconut Lime Shrimp Lo Mein with Bell Pepper & Sriracha
description: These saucy lo mein noodles—loaded with savory chicken and sweet bell pepper—are vibrant, fresh, and full of flavor. Coconut milk is the key to making a creamy sauce in a flash, while freshly squeezed lime juice adds brightness to this sweet-and-spicy dish. The best part? You’ll have it on the table in under 30 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67a9c4c14113630c74a344a4-1c75c9ec.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67ac4ec0e56e5cd8b0ac8ab8-en-US.pdf
